data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! Introducing your dream home in the sought-after Partridge Run neighborhood! This spacious 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom gem offers an exquisite inground pool, spacious concrete patio, and wonderful fire pit area that are the perfect setting for entertaining. The fire from the wood-burning fireplace is extra cozy on cold fall and winter nights. The massive garage provides ample space for your vehicles and storage needs. Conveniently located within walking distance from Shelby County schools. Don't miss the chance to make this your forever home, where relaxation and convenience meet!
